"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to AVIF format.</para>"
"<para>AV1 Image File Format is an image file format specification for storing images or image sequences compressed with AV1 in the ISOBMFF container format.</para>"
"<para>See details about this format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AVIF'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr ""

